body:
Ok, I succeed to solve the bug. Apprently, as @ajaun said an `__init__.py` file is missing in the "google" folder. Then, if I create an empty `__init__.py` file to get the following structure:

```
google
|-- __init__.py
|-- protobuf
```

It works.
